The Veturilo is compatible with [[Bemowo Bike]],<ref>{{en icon}} {{cite web |author= |url=http://en.veturilo.waw.pl/2012/07/30/veturilo-compatible-with-bemowo-bike-rental-systems/ |title=Veturilo compatible with Bemowo Bike rental systems |work=www.veturilo.waw.pl |publisher= |pages= |page= |date= |accessdate=2012-08-24}}</ref> a bicycle sharing system in the [[Bemowo]] district.

